Thank you for opening a new issue!

Please add the version of the Xtensions library you are using.

Also, please use the following tags according to the description given here:

* question: If no new or changed functionality is proposed, but a clarification is needed.
* enhancement : If an existing feature (e.g. a class or interface) should be enriched/extended.
* feature: If a new feature (e.g. a new extension method) should be added.
* bug: if an existing feature violates its contract or shows unexpected behavior.